{"id":511142,"date":[{"year":1971,"month":7,"day":4}],"page":"6","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"","column":"庆祝中国共产党诞生五十周年征文选刊,党的光辉照千秋","genre":"","count":"194","ytitle":"","mtitle":"一轮红日照胸怀","ftitle":"","authors":["罗兵"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"上海电机厂　罗兵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一步跨进大礼堂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"激情翻滚如海浪。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"仰望闪光主席台，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万丈金光照胸怀。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十年前情景怎能忘呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一股暖流万里长。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席登上主席台，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万岁声声震天外。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席和咱紧握手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"干劲如潮不断流。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席播下革命种，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“双水内冷”唱颂歌。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席挥手红烂漫，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"捷报如花四时开。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"站在礼堂望北京，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席和咱亲又近。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一轮红日心中升，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万马奔腾跨征程。"}]}